{"tid":1071443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥：本港樓價或續爆升，樓價高企令人擔憂，但每日150新移蝗鐵政不變","createTime":"2019-03-21T10:54:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T14:44:47.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9ba546679f1278d2c32478b86f980ccc1cf24b10","tid":1071443,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T10:54:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5c935ab9e60383d651fcc53b/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5c935ab9e60383d651fcc53b%2F&d=tFviIiuTv25K9aUiQ%2BXN3BVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=ec1d2519\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5c935ab9e60383d651fcc53b/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1443581-20190219.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1443581-20190219.htm&d=tFviIiuTv25K9aUiQ%2BXN3BVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=9771b95b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1443581-20190219.htm&h=346aeaff\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1443581-20190219.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥認為，樓價可能進一步上升，又指除非香港社會意識到解決樓價高企危機的逼切性，政府才能順利推行「明日大嶼」填海計劃，以增加土地供應。<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥說︰「(樓價高)的確令人擔憂，因為樓價已變得不可負擔，而將會變得更加不可負擔。除非香港社會感到逼切需要化解樓價(高企)危機，政府將難以推行增加土地供應計劃。我必須承認，政府需要在未來幾個月展示我們有能力管理(明日大嶼)基建計劃，從時間、預算方面。」<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥出席行政會議前被問到，有意見指每日150個單程證來港配額，加重本港醫療系統負擔，當局會否檢討審批政策。林鄭月娥回應說，單程證是家庭團聚制度，由內地審批，有關內地人是港人的親人，來港後成為香港居民，如果抽離地指他們用了多少香港醫療服務，是有排斥性的看法。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又說，根據數字，現時公立醫院使用率較高的是年長人士，但單程證來港屬年輕人士，因此可見有關說法並無準確基礎，呼籲大家用包容態度歡迎香港市民的家人來港團聚。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥重申，作為行政長官，須向香港負責亦向中央負責，她希望成為促進中央及香港關係正面發展的促成者，對於很少部分港人用負面、排斥性態度看待中央與香港關係，她感到失望，亦擔心影響其他市民的看法。"},{"pid":"ed91f6f155cee015c56d045795ba15c7cf0ae600","tid":1071443,"uid":243693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T11:19:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ccf6f7f5a9d07c7cef29b72bb87118d5196177f","tid":1071443,"uid":72085,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T11:23:42.000Z","msg":"即係間接承認政府為左推動超巨型基建而故意無為而治，等樓價升到爆？"},{"pid":"c89eb42661dc124826a849d469ec577c1543e0b4","tid":1071443,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T11:24:51.000Z","msg":"港共無為而治都還好<br />\n佢就係掉轉黎做"},{"pid":"712f5848a051199f593139d3eecf53d33b505189","tid":1071443,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T11:25:57.000Z","msg":"當樓價進一步失控時，不排除驅逐三十歲以上的本港永久居民到大灣區定居"},{"pid":"2c4dcfb8b2cd6a36bb5f142d400ce08e15832906","tid":1071443,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T11:27:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"3c357920e717bfffdfccaa30f7fca8adb72b7398","tid":1071443,"uid":62,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T11:29:33.000Z","msg":"來港團聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />難聽過粗口<br />\n無事帶黎嘅社會問題"},{"pid":"40b8dd776a17cf048ec3d1a6f2de863c55446ddc","tid":1071443,"uid":62,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T11:30:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>來港團聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />難聽過粗口<br />\n無<span style=\"color: red;\">視</span>帶黎嘅社會問題</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7de39479be1d8d24613c04d3bc9d6cf5c8478fe1","tid":1071443,"uid":201605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T11:32:34.000Z","msg":"「林鄭月娥又說，根據數字，現時公立醫院使用率較高的是年長人士，但單程證來港屬年輕人士，因此可見有關說法並無準確基礎」<br />\ncome on，劍橋畢業架，畀少少logic 好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d1c4574e938d39c37e5c170d715cf1dc1c51355","tid":1071443,"uid":52059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T11:36:27.000Z","msg":"增加土地供應唔會降低樓價<br />\n私樓已經唔係普通商品跟隨基本供求定律"},{"pid":"ffc0a39cbc0867eb5fd4652abb25adab10ea00e3","tid":1071443,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T11:37:58.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n林病連因果都未搞清楚"},{"pid":"d3e009b687c98b0b0ac9aead4565dd2b49bf3f0d","tid":1071443,"uid":206895,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T11:38:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Guw4O5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Guw4O5.gif&h=3ffc1b8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b8d4d91e10a8edbae2364a19396726125422a19","tid":1071443,"uid":44415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3e009b687c98b0b0ac9aead4565dd2b49bf3f0d","tid":1071443,"uid":206895,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T11:38:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Guw4O5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Guw4O5.gif&h=3ffc1b8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T11:40:24.000Z","msg":"好治癒"},{"pid":"78672748a87c2d438e4c92089f83a8e3aff9b9e8","tid":1071443,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T14:15:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e35dc5a11134916d6ce583e0bfe1f7a2e9447ab4","tid":1071443,"uid":13936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T14:23:36.000Z","msg":"政府想谷樓價爆上去 有藉口推大愚 好仆街呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c6533b270c772562672923e16a9d4d6d2016f4","tid":1071443,"uid":84302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T14:28:42.000Z","msg":"中聯辦班撚樣，日撚日諗埋哂d屎橋cap水<br />\n每日150名額先cap 一水<br />\n分化香港再支埋維穩費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b185fcd6ee846c6f309eea3522e90c2c3b6cecc7","tid":1071443,"uid":26773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T14:29:10.000Z","msg":"150係咁多年黎既政治任務<br />\n到佢手就斷 唔比阿爺屌死？"},{"pid":"1bbd2a2424b24456b31a261f934f5931c7